WEBVTT

10:31.380 --> 10:34.342
It has been
five days since my last confession.

10:34.842 --> 10:37.803
-I took the Lord's name in vain.
-

10:39.347 --> 10:41.265
Three times that I remember.

10:42.558 --> 10:44.602
I kicked Silvia's dog.

10:46.604 --> 10:49.190
I was short-tempered with my children.

10:49.273 --> 10:50.983
Rafael especially.

10:54.362 --> 10:58.115
Bon-Bon is
too small to be kicked.

10:58.199 --> 11:01.202
Yes. But Silvia lets her in my office.

11:01.285 --> 11:03.204
She gets under my feet.

11:03.287 --> 11:05.706
- So pick her up.
-

11:05.790 --> 11:09.001
She's a good dog.

11:10.461 --> 11:11.379
I'll try.

11:12.922 --> 11:17.760
Andâ€¦ apologize to Rafael.

11:18.511 --> 11:21.305
He'll learn more from that
than your anger.

11:21.389 --> 11:23.349
My anger makes him strong.

11:23.974 --> 11:27.103
And shortens his childhood.

11:27.186 --> 11:29.397
Let him have it a little longer.

11:35.444 --> 11:37.863
I have to return this.

11:39.490 --> 11:44.704
I am sorry
for having offended thee, my God.

11:44.787 --> 11:49.667
I detest my sins because they offend you.

11:49.750 --> 11:53.087
I resolve, with thy grace, to do penance

11:53.170 --> 11:56.465
and avoid the near occasion of sin.

11:56.549 --> 11:59.218
In the name of the Father,
Son, and Holy Ghost

11:59.301 --> 12:01.512
I absolve you of these sins.

12:06.100 --> 12:07.685
Any other confessions?

13:24.845 --> 13:26.889
- Was that Marty Byrde?
-Yes.

13:29.266 --> 13:33.187
Please tell me he has
the hillbilly bitch in line?

13:33.270 --> 13:36.357
These Byrdes are so disrespectful.

13:36.440 --> 13:38.818
Helen would have fixed this immediately.

13:42.696 --> 13:44.490
Are you joking, Javi?

13:46.784 --> 13:49.286
You nearly fucked us with your impatience.

13:52.164 --> 13:56.752
If they connect that sheriff to us,

13:58.128 --> 14:00.881
the FBI will come down here
just like they did with Lagunas.

14:00.965 --> 14:05.302
Then you will have all our blood

14:05.386 --> 14:07.888
on your soft little hands, Javi.

14:10.683 --> 14:12.601
I was careful. They'll never know.

14:12.685 --> 14:15.938
Oh, Javi was careful.

14:18.274 --> 14:21.026
With all his years of experience.

14:23.529 --> 14:25.197
He protected us all.

14:27.074 --> 14:29.910
Or did you leave it
for somebody else to clean up? Huh?

14:29.994 --> 14:31.412
It'll be taken care of.

14:33.789 --> 14:34.665
All of it.

14:47.052 --> 14:48.888
Now the baby is sad.
